        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2601358372" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer18142000376553477545">Nice message but the plot was so cheesy, cliche and forced I don’t think it could even be made into a Lifetime movie.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


